name: Pinups Skull Clutch Bag
description:
Flaunt your punk rock style with this faux crocodile grain SKULL clutch! Features a bling skull head on the envelope flap closure, high gloss finish and has a strap that can be added to make it a shoulder bag or wristlet! It measures 12" across, 6" in height and .5" wide. 
Magnetic snap closure, interior pocket and cell phone holder.
